Codes for downloading data from the necessary data:

Downloading a pdb file
wget https://files.rcsb.org/download/1B17.cif.gz


Anaconda
mkdir -p ~/miniconda3
wget https://repo.anaconda.com/miniconda/Miniconda3-latest-Linux-x86_64.sh -O ~/miniconda3/miniconda.sh
bash ~/miniconda3/miniconda.sh -b -u -p ~/miniconda3
rm ~/miniconda3/miniconda.sh

After installing, close and reopen your terminal application or refresh it by running the following command:
source ~/miniconda3/bin/activate

Then, initialize conda on all available shells by running the following command:
conda init --all




Gromacs

wget https://ftp.gromacs.org/gromacs/gromacs-2025.1.tar.gz
